channel.title: PI how i get more than 13m xp
channel.description: my xp won't go up than 13m, I changed max levels to 200 and max exp to 500m and I tried also 200m but doesnt work.. is there something I need to touch client sided?

item.title: PI how i get more than 13m xp
item.dc:creator: @Vain1 Vain_
item.description:
@Vain1 wrote:

The client may have a custom skill interfaces. Some kids before have limited the interface string to not display more than 13034431. So if the server has the xp but won’t show on interface, it may be client sided. If the player files won’t get more than 13034431, then it’s the server.
